They all were helpful & kind however not one knew that this does not apply for a grandparent.  I put the claim in & a couple days later I was called & told my claim had been denied. I think someone should have known that. Since I’m filling out this survey I also filed a claim @ 3 years ago my husband was having problems also & I was denied then also so I’m not real impressed by this program. I would think a grandfather is family
